examples.en: The building was defaced with graffiti.
The desk was covered with graffiti and burn marks.
Buildings old and new are thickly covered with graffiti.
The graffiti on the wall said 'Liverpool rules OK'.
A group of vandals broke into the school and painted graffiti on the walls.
Vandals desecrated the cemetery last night by covering the tombstones with graffiti.
